<?php

namespace App\Models;

use App\Models\Traits\ModelAttributes;

class Comment extends BaseModel
{
    use ModelAttributes;
    protected $tale = 'voxo_media_comments';
    /**
     * Fillable.
     *
     * @var array
     */
    protected $fillable = [
        'user_id',
        'post_id',
        'content',
        'image',
        'emoji',
    ];

    /**
     * Dates.
     *
     * @var array
     */
    protected $dates = [
        'created_at',
        'updated_at',
    ];
}
